cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.IT 

This paper deals with key management in wireless networks, which is a core concern in computer security (cs.CR). The paper specifically focuses on self-healing key distribution, which is a key issue in mobile wireless networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the efficiency of the proposed scheme, which falls under the category of distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper proposes a scheme that achieves forward and backward secrecy, which is a topic in systems and control (cs.SY) and information theory (cs.IT).
